{"in": {"title": "STUFFED by Mark Keavney", "subtitle": "<div>1 INT. MCFIDDLEY WORKSHOP - 1980S - DUSK</div>", "lines": ["SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/radio-news-40s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "NARRATOR: A SQUIRREL stands on a workbench.", "HANNAH (O.S.): (x-slow) Whats this one do?", "JEDIDIAH (O.S.): You'll see! (pause)", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/desk-foley-9s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "NARRATOR: JEDIDIAH, 40s, bursting with nervous energy, picks up the squirrel, revealing that it's dead and stuffed. He opens the squirrels back and shoves in a mini-cassette. He struggles to get it to fit, then finally jams it in.", "NARRATOR: He puts the squirrel back on the workbench. It falls over.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/crashing-down-4s.mp3", "JEDIDIAH: Hold on! (pause)", "NARRATOR: Jedidiah's workshop is filled with dead animals and mechanical technology thrown together on shelves and tables, or built into each other. There's a taxidermied boar with a crank sticking out of its head, a cuckoo clock decorated with dead birds, and a baby skunk perfume dispenser. Taxidermy is also part of the furniture here - the tables have deer legs and the doorknobs are hooves.", "NARRATOR: A cannonball sits on a shelf directly above the squirrel.", "NARRATOR: Jedidiah's FIVE CHILDREN, mostly bored, sit facing the squirrel. Jedidiah frantically stands it up again.", "NARRATOR: HANNAH, 18, is rebellious and distracted.", "HANNAH: (slow) Do I have to be here?", "NARRATOR: EVE, 16, is pretty and jealous.", "EVE: If she dont have to be here, then I shouldnt have to be here either.", "JEDIDIAH: Come on, you used to love this.", "HANNAH: Yeah, when I was six.", "NARRATOR: MATTHEW, 12, is admiring and eager.", "MATTHEW: I love it, Pa! I want to see what it does.", "JEDIDIAH: Thank you, Matthew. I appreciate the support.", "NARRATOR: Eve rolls her eyes.", "NARRATOR: OLDER SON, 14, is pudgy and sullen. YOUNGEST DAUGHTER, 9, is happy and curious.", "JEDIDIAH: OK, here we go!", "NARRATOR: He flips a switch in the squirrel's back.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/switch-flip-500ms.mp3", "NARRATOR: (pause) Nothing happens.", "EVE: (sarcastic) Wow. (pause)", "NARRATOR: Jedidiah fiddles some more.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/misc-foley-2s.mp3", "NARRATOR: Finally a small, tinny rendition of the song \"I will survive\" by Gloria Gaynor plays from the squirrel. Its mouth moves with the music.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/gaynor-afraid-12s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "NARRATOR: Matthew smiles. The teenagers are still bored.", "JEDIDIAH: (pause) Wait - there's more!", "NARRATOR: The song continues, and the squirrel starts a jerky mechanical dance. Jedidiah dances with it, badly, and motions his children to join him. No one does.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/gaynor-chipmunk-clip-30s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/crash-fall-2.5s.mp3", "NARRATOR: The squirrel dances off the edge of the workbench.", "NARRATOR: Jedidiah picks it up and desperately puts it back. He looks to his children and sees that he's lost them, but he's got one last trick.", "JEDIDIAH: Listen to this! (pause)", "NARRATOR: He plugs an audio cable into the squirrel's hindquarters. Suddenly the song booms out from speakers all around the children, very loud.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/gaynor-walk-out-15s.mp3 (no wait)", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", "NARRATOR: The children cover their ears."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Matthew", "SCENE": "Matthew", "TITLE": "Joanna", "SMALL VOICE": "Raveena", "FANGS": "Brian", "PEONY": "Raveena", "HANNAH (O.S.)": "Joanna", "JEDIDIAH (O.S.)": "Joanna", "JEDIDIAH": "Joanna", "HANNAH": "Joanna", "EVE": "Joanna", "MATTHEW": "Joanna"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "85c01ca861dd3e1229f3e614eec17223", "audio_objects": [["https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/radio-news-40s.mp3", 1], ["https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", 0], ["f0aa17069386ec29b3bf40c1eb0a36e4-a-squirrel-stands-on-a-wo---", 0], ["d80d7c461fca740ce81fabcd94cb172b--whats-this-one-do-", 0], ["cedf8fd713b42cec68a89642b507bcd7-you-ll-see--", 0], ["https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/desk-foley-9s.mp3", 1], ["https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/misc/silence-5s.mp3", 0], ["89f9a366dbe463f0a5b67f292b9f2788-jedidiah--40s--bursting-w---", 0], ["76e779a98c36c98a6e9b87d8985f4cbd-he-puts-the-squirrel-back---", 0], ["https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/stuffed/crashing-down-4s.mp3", 0], ["eb0b0952cea8b562c06f2b16d264493b-hold-on--", 0], ["8ee801d39e9456a2fd2d9ba7bdc81eda-jedidiah-s-workshop-is-fi---", 0], ["4645d2bbb7db8714a85f8fb0caf01a71-a-cannonball-sits-on-a-sh---", 0], ["bab3b0cfb6296d983dce775ef48e7411-jedidiah-s-five-children----", 0], ["0f23e5b0908da0cb579a927084dff3c3-hannah--18--is-rebellious---", 0], ["5ceab837557aa43c37529601fd8f102b--do-i-have-to-be-here-", 0], ["6f130f8e50cd540a402af0e4d5dff31b-eve--16--is-pretty-and-je---", 0], ["1eda049f143e47510d36687cada4fa54-if-she-dont-have-to-be-he---", 0], ["5a111471d87f264bdb988f4f17b84f0f-come-on--you-used-to-love---", 0], ["0f6d1bff45791677fd6c520ea2ac222e-yeah--whe